{
  "stem": "22582.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were not assigned to stay in Gross-Rosen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They usually took people, like a staging, like a camp.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they distributed to different camps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Unless you were staying there for a steady, then they are-- you know, first day, you came-- when you came in, and the-- and the entrance was [SPEAKING GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The-- you-- the work makes you free.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the-- the-- the music was on-- at-- at the gate.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we were so surprised.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I never heard so music.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Music, some kind-- you know, like a band.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the guy-- and the guys who were-- usually, they-- I think they were Volksdeutsches or some Ukrainians or [INAUDIBLE], from Latvia, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The people were guarding us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they said, this was a-- this was Volksdeutsche.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know, a Volksdeutsche was a man who was of German descent.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they said, oh, you have it German.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "No, that's-- that's a bad camp when music is  staying at the gate.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So right there, they took us to [INAUDIBLE] to clean up whatever we had, in case we have some fleas or whatever.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- they shaved our heads and shaved our everywhere.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we're naked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We came out naked on the side of the-- of the barracks, where [INAUDIBLE] was.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then they started to look what we have, what else.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had this ring.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I didn't know what to do with it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So being I was naked, completely naked, and they were looking in the ears and everywhere.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I-- I-- I had teeth at the time, good teeth.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I-- I somehow broke the ring-- and-- and swallowed the diamond.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- and then they gave us the striped pants like a pajamas.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That's what we wore, or had.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then they assigned us to barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
